Implement a PHP program that creates sessions, sets values in sessions, and removes data from
the sessions.

SOLUTION:
A PHP program that demonstrates:
Creating sessions
Storing values in sessions
Removing session data

CODE:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>PHP Session Example</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Session Handling in PHP</h2>
    <a href="?set=true">Set Session Variables</a><br>
    <a href="?show=true">Show Session Variables</a><br>
    <a href="?remove=true">Remove 'role' Variable</a><br>
    <a href="?destroy=true">Destroy Session</a><br>
</body>
</html>
